{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":651,"text":"It was a Saturday afternoon in May,"},{"time":3830,"text":"and I suddenly realized"},{"time":6344,"text":"that the next day was Mother's Day,"},{"time":9798,"text":"and I hadn't gotten anything for my mom,"},{"time":11644,"text":"so I started thinking about"},{"time":13045,"text":"what should I get my mom for Mother's Day?"},{"time":15382,"text":"I thought, why don't I make her"},{"time":17226,"text":"an interactive Mother's Day card"},{"time":20275,"text":"using the Scratch software that I'd been developing"},{"time":22983,"text":"with my research group at the MIT Media Lab?"},{"time":26800,"text":"We developed it so that people could easily create"},{"time":30180,"text":"their own interactive stories and games and animations,"},{"time":34424,"text":"and then share their creations with one another."},{"time":38193,"text":"So I thought, this would be an opportunity to use Scratch"},{"time":42061,"text":"to make an interactive card for my mom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44961,"text":"Before making my own Mother's Day card,"},{"time":47137,"text":"I thought I would take a look"},{"time":49122,"text":"at the Scratch website."},{"time":50695,"text":"So over the last several years, kids around the world"},{"time":54053,"text":"ages 8 and up, have shared their projects,"},{"time":57247,"text":"and I thought, I wonder if, of those three million projects,"},{"time":60682,"text":"whether anyone else has thought to put up Mother's Day cards."},{"time":64067,"text":"So in the search box I typed in"},{"time":67061,"text":"\"Mother's Day,\""},{"time":68606,"text":"and I was surprised and delighted to see a list"},{"time":71609,"text":"of dozens and dozens of Mother's Day cards"},{"time":74313,"text":"that showed up on the Scratch website,"},{"time":76827,"text":"many of them just in the past 24 hours"},{"time":79145,"text":"by procrastinators just like myself."},{"time":82351,"text":"So I started taking a look at them. (Music)"},{"time":85473,"text":"I saw one of them that featured a kitten"},{"time":87929,"text":"and her mom and wishing her mom a happy Mother's Day."},{"time":94800,"text":"And the creator very considerately"},{"time":97331,"text":"offered a replay for her mom."},{"time":100835,"text":"Another one was an interactive project where,"},{"time":103219,"text":"when you moved the mouse over the letters of \"Happy Mom Day,\""},{"time":106417,"text":"it reveals a special happy Mother's Day slogan."},{"time":111337,"text":"(Music) In this one, the creator told a narrative"},{"time":115320,"text":"about how she had Googled to find out"},{"time":117979,"text":"when Mother's Day was happening."},{"time":121096,"text":"(Typing) And then once she found out when Mother's Day was happening,"},{"time":125239,"text":"she delivered a special Mother's Day greeting"},{"time":127717,"text":"of how much she loved her mom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131344,"text":"So I really enjoyed looking at these projects"},{"time":133569,"text":"and interacting with these projects."},{"time":135221,"text":"In fact, I liked it so much that, instead of making my own project,"},{"time":139062,"text":"I sent my mom links to about a dozen of these projects. (Laughter)"},{"time":143816,"text":"And actually, she reacted exactly the way that I hoped that she would."},{"time":147396,"text":"She wrote back to me and she said,"},{"time":148781,"text":"\"I'm so proud to have a son that created the software"},{"time":152048,"text":"that allowed these kids to make Mother's Day cards for their mothers.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":156160,"text":"So my mom was happy, and that made me happy,"},{"time":159960,"text":"but actually I was even happier for another reason."},{"time":164584,"text":"I was happy because these kids were using Scratch"},{"time":168543,"text":"just in the way that we had hoped that they would."},{"time":171344,"text":"As they created their interactive Mother's Day cards,"},{"time":174155,"text":"you could see that they were really"},{"time":176436,"text":"becoming fluent with new technologies."},{"time":179748,"text":"What do I mean by fluent?"},{"time":181211,"text":"I mean that they were able to start expressing themselves"},{"time":185243,"text":"and to start expressing their ideas."},{"time":188020,"text":"When you become fluent with language,"},{"time":190674,"text":"it means you can write an entry in your journal"},{"time":194211,"text":"or tell a joke to someone or write a letter to a friend."},{"time":198264,"text":"And it's similar with new technologies."},{"time":201421,"text":"By writing, be creating these interactive Mother's Day cards,"},{"time":205603,"text":"these kids were showing that they were really fluent"},{"time":208133,"text":"with new technologies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209806,"text":"Now maybe you won't be so surprised by this,"},{"time":212571,"text":"because a lot of times people feel that"},{"time":215267,"text":"young people today can do all sorts of things with technology."},{"time":218667,"text":"I mean, all of us have heard young people referred to as \"digital natives.\""},{"time":223128,"text":"But actually I'm sort of skeptical about this term."},{"time":226925,"text":"I'm not so sure we should be thinking of young people as digital natives."},{"time":230426,"text":"When you really look at it, how is it that young people"},{"time":232979,"text":"spend most of their time using new technologies?"},{"time":236515,"text":"You often see them in situations like this,"},{"time":240038,"text":"or like this,"},{"time":242232,"text":"and there's no doubt that young people"},{"time":243750,"text":"are very comfortable and familiar browsing"},{"time":247066,"text":"and chatting and texting and gaming."},{"time":251588,"text":"But that doesn't really make you fluent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":254787,"text":"So young people today have lots of experience"},{"time":258746,"text":"and lots of familiarity with interacting with new technologies,"},{"time":262541,"text":"but a lot less so of creating with new technologies"},{"time":265946,"text":"and expressing themselves with new technologies."},{"time":268918,"text":"It's almost as if they can read"},{"time":271310,"text":"but not write with new technologies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274643,"text":"And I'm really interested in seeing, how can we help young people become fluent"},{"time":278541,"text":"so they can write with new technologies?"},{"time":281070,"text":"And that really means that they need to be able to"},{"time":284430,"text":"write their own computer programs, or code."}]},{"cues":[{"time":288942,"text":"So, increasingly, people are starting to recognize"},{"time":291654,"text":"the importance of learning to code."},{"time":294958,"text":"You know, in recent years, there have been"},{"time":297560,"text":"hundreds of new organizations and websites"},{"time":300452,"text":"that are helping young people learn to code."},{"time":303746,"text":"You look online, you'll see places like Codecademy"},{"time":307337,"text":"and events like CoderDojo"},{"time":309708,"text":"and sites like Girls Who Code,"},{"time":312139,"text":"or Black Girls Code."},{"time":313833,"text":"It seems that everybody is getting into the act."},{"time":316941,"text":"You know, just at the beginning of this year,"},{"time":319524,"text":"at the turn of the new year,"},{"time":320889,"text":"New York City Mayor Michael Bloomberg"},{"time":323549,"text":"made a New Year's resolution that he was going to learn"},{"time":325809,"text":"to code in 2012."},{"time":328588,"text":"A few months later, the country of Estonia decided that"},{"time":331756,"text":"all of its first graders should learn to code."},{"time":335412,"text":"And that triggered a debate in the U.K."},{"time":338204,"text":"about whether all the children there should learn to code."}]},{"cues":[{"time":342513,"text":"Now, for some of you, when you hear about this,"},{"time":345356,"text":"it might seem sort of strange about everybody learning to code."},{"time":348964,"text":"When many people think of coding, they think of it"},{"time":352114,"text":"as something that only a very narrow sub-community"},{"time":355690,"text":"of people are going to be doing,"},{"time":358348,"text":"and they think of coding looking like this."},{"time":361270,"text":"And in fact, if this is what coding is like,"},{"time":363436,"text":"it will only be a narrow sub-community of people"},{"time":365931,"text":"with special mathematical skills and technological background"},{"time":369003,"text":"that can code."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371269,"text":"But coding doesn't have to be like this."},{"time":373769,"text":"Let me show you about what it's like to code in Scratch."},{"time":377748,"text":"So in Scratch, to code, you just snap blocks together."},{"time":382027,"text":"In this case, you take a move block,"},{"time":383942,"text":"snap it into a stack,"},{"time":385711,"text":"and the stacks of blocks control the behaviors"},{"time":388469,"text":"of the different characters in your game or your story,"},{"time":391987,"text":"in this case controlling the big fish."},{"time":394288,"text":"After you've created your program, you can click on \"share,\""},{"time":397739,"text":"and then share your project with other people,"},{"time":400815,"text":"so that they can use the project"},{"time":402638,"text":"and start working on the project as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":405612,"text":"So, of course, making a fish game isn't the only thing"},{"time":408934,"text":"you can do with Scratch."},{"time":410579,"text":"Of the millions of projects on the Scratch website,"},{"time":412559,"text":"there's everything from animated stories"},{"time":415383,"text":"to school science projects"},{"time":417799,"text":"to anime soap operas"},{"time":419863,"text":"to virtual construction kits"},{"time":422185,"text":"to recreations of classic video games"},{"time":424898,"text":"to political opinion polls"},{"time":427167,"text":"to trigonometry tutorials"},{"time":429807,"text":"to interactive artwork, and, yes,"},{"time":432727,"text":"interactive Mother's Day cards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435511,"text":"So I think there's so many different ways"},{"time":438547,"text":"that people can express themselves using this,"},{"time":442007,"text":"to be able to take their ideas and share their ideas with the world."},{"time":445407,"text":"And it doesn't just stay on the screen."},{"time":447969,"text":"You can also code to interact with the physical world around you."},{"time":451736,"text":"Here's an example from Hong Kong,"},{"time":454215,"text":"where some kids made a game"},{"time":455622,"text":"and then built their own physical interface device"},{"time":458903,"text":"and had a light sensor, so the light sensor"},{"time":461795,"text":"detects the hole in the board,"},{"time":463738,"text":"so as they move the physical saw,"},{"time":465938,"text":"the light sensor detects the hole"},{"time":468178,"text":"and controls the virtual saw on the screen"},{"time":471134,"text":"and saws down the tree."}]},{"cues":[{"time":473914,"text":"We're going to continue to look at new ways"},{"time":476023,"text":"of bringing together the physical world and the virtual world"},{"time":479079,"text":"and connecting to the world around us."},{"time":482007,"text":"This is an example from a new version of Scratch"},{"time":484240,"text":"that we'll be releasing in the next few months,"},{"time":487863,"text":"and we're looking again to be able"},{"time":489913,"text":"to push you in new directions."},{"time":491609,"text":"Here's an example."},{"time":493873,"text":"It uses the webcam."},{"time":497947,"text":"And as I move my hand, I can pop the balloons"},{"time":502803,"text":"or I can move the bug."},{"time":505688,"text":"So it's a little bit like Microsoft Kinect,"},{"time":508253,"text":"where you interact with gestures in the world."},{"time":510969,"text":"But instead of just playing someone else's game,"},{"time":513213,"text":"you get to create the games,"},{"time":515455,"text":"and if you see someone else's game,"},{"time":516838,"text":"you can just say \"see inside,\""},{"time":519478,"text":"and you can look at the stacks of blocks that control it."},{"time":522372,"text":"So there's a new block that says how much video motion there is,"},{"time":525927,"text":"and then, if there's so much video motion,"},{"time":529048,"text":"it will then tell the balloon to pop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":532427,"text":"The same way that this uses the camera"},{"time":534811,"text":"to get information into Scratch,"},{"time":537316,"text":"you can also use the microphone."},{"time":540323,"text":"Here's an example of a project using the microphone."},{"time":544307,"text":"So I'm going to let all of you control this game"},{"time":546707,"text":"using your voices."}]},{"cues":[{"time":548953,"text":"(Crickets chirping) (Shouts) (Chomping)"},{"time":565409,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":574038,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":582822,"text":"As kids are creating projects like this,"},{"time":585427,"text":"they're learning to code,"},{"time":587692,"text":"but even more importantly, they're coding to learn."},{"time":591626,"text":"Because as they learn to code,"},{"time":593915,"text":"it enables them to learn many other things,"},{"time":597235,"text":"opens up many new opportunities for learning."},{"time":600107,"text":"Again, it's useful to make an analogy to reading and writing."},{"time":604491,"text":"When you learn to read and write, it opens up"},{"time":607431,"text":"opportunities for you to learn so many other things."},{"time":610491,"text":"When you learn to read, you can then read to learn."},{"time":614251,"text":"And it's the same thing with coding."},{"time":616439,"text":"If you learn to code, you can code to learn."},{"time":618986,"text":"Now some of the things you can learn are sort of obvious."},{"time":621540,"text":"You learn more about how computers work."},{"time":624038,"text":"But that's just where it starts."},{"time":626356,"text":"When you learn to code, it opens up for you to learn"},{"time":628951,"text":"many other things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":631196,"text":"Let me show you an example."},{"time":633542,"text":"Here's another project,"},{"time":635812,"text":"and I saw this when I was visiting"},{"time":638080,"text":"one of the computer clubhouses."},{"time":640222,"text":"These are after-school learning centers that we helped start"},{"time":643242,"text":"that help young people from low-income communities"},{"time":646004,"text":"learn to express themselves creatively with new technologies."},{"time":650083,"text":"And when I went to one of the clubhouses a couple years ago,"},{"time":652878,"text":"I saw a 13-year-old boy who was using our Scratch software"},{"time":656603,"text":"to create a game somewhat like this one,"},{"time":659499,"text":"and he was very happy with his game and proud of his game,"},{"time":662422,"text":"but also he wanted to do more."},{"time":665387,"text":"He wanted to keep score."},{"time":667691,"text":"So this was a game where the big fish eats the little fish,"},{"time":670767,"text":"but he wanted to keep score, so that each time"},{"time":673694,"text":"the big fish eats the little fish,"},{"time":677072,"text":"the score would go up and it would keep track,"},{"time":679611,"text":"and he didn't know how to do that."},{"time":682123,"text":"So I showed him."},{"time":684388,"text":"In Scratch, you can create something called a variable."},{"time":687965,"text":"I'll call it score."},{"time":692092,"text":"And that creates some new blocks for you,"},{"time":694923,"text":"and also creates a little scoreboard that keeps track of the score,"},{"time":699589,"text":"so each time I click on \"change score,\" it increments the score."},{"time":704841,"text":"So I showed this to the clubhouse member --"},{"time":707366,"text":"let's call him Victor -- and Victor,"},{"time":710067,"text":"when he saw that this block would let him increment the score,"},{"time":712869,"text":"he knew exactly what to do."},{"time":714685,"text":"He took the block"},{"time":716999,"text":"and he put it into the program"},{"time":720043,"text":"exactly where the big fish eats the little fish."},{"time":724236,"text":"So then, each time the big fish eats the little fish,"},{"time":729259,"text":"he will increment the score, and the score will go up by one."},{"time":735254,"text":"And it's in fact working."},{"time":736951,"text":"And he saw this, and he was so excited,"},{"time":739205,"text":"he reached his hand out to me,"},{"time":740884,"text":"and he said, \"Thank you, thank you, thank you.\""},{"time":743433,"text":"And what went through my mind was,"},{"time":745502,"text":"how often is it that teachers are thanked by their students"},{"time":748544,"text":"for teaching them variables? (Laughter)"},{"time":751947,"text":"It doesn't happen in most classrooms,"},{"time":754428,"text":"but that's because in most classrooms, when kids learn about variables,"},{"time":757387,"text":"they don't know why they're learning it."},{"time":759895,"text":"It's nothing that, really, they can make use of."},{"time":762766,"text":"When you learn ideas like this in Scratch,"},{"time":764928,"text":"you can learn it in a way that's really meaningful and motivating for you,"},{"time":769031,"text":"that you can understand the reason for learning variables,"},{"time":772021,"text":"and we see that kids learn it more deeply"},{"time":774063,"text":"and learn it better."},{"time":775478,"text":"Victor had, I'm sure, been taught about variables in schools,"},{"time":778519,"text":"but he really didn't -- he wasn't paying attention."},{"time":780707,"text":"Now he had a reason for learning variables."},{"time":782990,"text":"So when you learn through coding, and coding to learn,"},{"time":786064,"text":"you're learning it in a meaningful context, and that's the best way of learning things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":790948,"text":"So as kids like Victor are creating projects like this,"},{"time":794403,"text":"they're learning important concepts like variables,"},{"time":797187,"text":"but that's just the start."},{"time":799315,"text":"As Victor worked on this project and created the scripts,"},{"time":803165,"text":"he was also learning about the process of design,"},{"time":806417,"text":"how to start with the glimmer of an idea"},{"time":809036,"text":"and turn it into a fully-fledged, functioning project"},{"time":811942,"text":"like you see here."},{"time":814449,"text":"So he was learning many different core principles of design,"},{"time":818489,"text":"about how to experiment with new ideas,"},{"time":821731,"text":"how to take complex ideas and break them down into simpler parts,"},{"time":826436,"text":"how to collaborate with other people on your projects,"},{"time":829426,"text":"about how to find and fix bugs when things go wrong,"},{"time":832877,"text":"how to keep persistent and to persevere"},{"time":835931,"text":"in the face of frustrations when things aren't working well."},{"time":839336,"text":"Now those are important skills"},{"time":841109,"text":"that aren't just relevant for coding."},{"time":843977,"text":"They're relevant for all sorts of different activities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":846804,"text":"Now, who knows if Victor is going to grow up and become"},{"time":849972,"text":"a programmer or a professional computer scientist?"},{"time":852896,"text":"It's probably not so likely,"},{"time":854708,"text":"but regardless of what he does,"},{"time":856496,"text":"he'll be able to make use of these design skills that he learned."},{"time":860200,"text":"Regardless of whether he grows up to be a marketing manager"},{"time":862784,"text":"or a mechanic or a community organizer,"},{"time":865904,"text":"that these ideas are useful for everybody."},{"time":868360,"text":"Again, it's useful to think about this analogy with language."},{"time":872282,"text":"When you become fluent with reading and writing,"},{"time":876638,"text":"it's not something that you're doing"},{"time":879079,"text":"just to become a professional writer."},{"time":881039,"text":"Very few people become professional writers."},{"time":883736,"text":"But it's useful for everybody to learn how to read and write."},{"time":887304,"text":"Again, the same thing with coding."},{"time":889399,"text":"Most people won't grow up to become professional"},{"time":891621,"text":"computer scientists or programmers,"},{"time":894840,"text":"but those skills of thinking creatively,"},{"time":897178,"text":"reasoning systematically, working collaboratively --"},{"time":899692,"text":"skills you develop when you code in Scratch --"},{"time":902402,"text":"are things that people can use no matter what they're doing in their work lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":907224,"text":"And it's not just about your work life."},{"time":909600,"text":"Coding can also enable you to"},{"time":912320,"text":"express your ideas and feelings in your personal life."},{"time":915496,"text":"Let me end with just one more example."},{"time":918169,"text":"So this is an example that came from"},{"time":921296,"text":"after I had sent the Mother's Day cards to my mom,"},{"time":925764,"text":"she decided that she wanted to learn Scratch."},{"time":928865,"text":"So she made this project for my birthday"},{"time":931896,"text":"and sent me a happy birthday Scratch card."},{"time":935472,"text":"Now this project is not going to win any prizes for design,"},{"time":939328,"text":"and you can rest assured that my 83-year-old mom"},{"time":942303,"text":"is not training to become a professional programmer or computer scientist."},{"time":946540,"text":"But working on this project enabled her"},{"time":949512,"text":"to make a connection to someone that she cares about"},{"time":952178,"text":"and enabled her to keep on learning new things"},{"time":954986,"text":"and continuing to practice her creativity"},{"time":957418,"text":"and developing new ways of expressing herself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":960593,"text":"So as we take a look and we see that"},{"time":964804,"text":"Michael Bloomberg is learning to code,"},{"time":967368,"text":"all of the children of Estonia learn to code,"},{"time":970018,"text":"even my mom has learned to code,"},{"time":972218,"text":"don't you think it's about time that you might be"},{"time":973990,"text":"thinking about learning to code?"},{"time":975902,"text":"If you're interested in giving it a try,"},{"time":978095,"text":"I'd encourage you to go to the Scratch website."},{"time":980531,"text":"It's scratch.mit.edu,"},{"time":982556,"text":"and give a try at coding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":984378,"text":"Thanks very much. (Applause)"}]}]}